trans-unit.source: Camera is a special node that displays what is visible from its current location. Cameras register themselves in the nearest Viewport node (when ascending the tree). Only one camera can be active per viewport. If no viewport is available ascending the tree, the Camera will register in the global viewport. In other words, a Camera just provides 3D display capabilities to a Viewport, and, without one, a scene registered in that Viewport (or higher viewports) can’t be displayed.

trans-unit.source: Create client that connects to a server at address using specified port. The given address needs to be either a fully qualified domain name (e.g. www.example.com) or an IP address in IPv4 or IPv6 format (e.g. 192.168.1.1). The port is the port the server is listening on. The in_bandwidth and out_bandwidth parameters can be used to limit the incoming and outgoing bandwidth to the given number of bytes per second. The default of 0 means unlimited bandwidth. Note that ENet will strategically drop packets on specific sides of a connection between peers to ensure the peer’s bandwidth is not overwhelmed. The bandwidth parameters also determine the window size of a connection which limits the amount of reliable packets that may be in transit at any given time. Returns @GlobalScope.OK if a client was created, @GlobalScope.ERR_ALREADY_IN_USE if this NetworkedMultiplayerEnet instance already has an open connection (in which case you need to call close_connection first) or @GlobalScope.ERR_CANT_CREATE if the client could not be created. If client_port is specified, the client will also listen to the given port, this is useful in some NAT traversal technique.

The default IP is the wildcard *, which listens on all available interfaces. max_clients is the maximum number of clients that are allowed at once, any number up to 4096 may be used, although the achievable number of simultaneous clients may be far lower and depends on the application. trans-unit.source: Emitted immediately before Node._physics_process is called on every node in the SceneTree.
trans-unit.target: 在SceneTree中的每个节点上调用Node._physics_process之前立即 SceneTree 。

trans-unit.source: Emitted immediately before Node._process is called on every node in the SceneTree.
trans-unit.target: 在SceneTree中的每个节点上调用Node._process之前立即 SceneTree 。

trans-unit.source: Emitted instead of item_selected when select_mode is SELECT_MULTI.
trans-unit.target: 发出的，而不是 item_selected 时 select_mode 是SELECT_MULTI。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when frame changed.
trans-unit.target: 框架改变时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when frame changed.
trans-unit.target: 框架改变时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when _input_event receives an event. See its description for details.
trans-unit.target: 在_input_event接收事件时发出。有关详细信息，请参见其说明。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when max_value or min_value is changed.
trans-unit.target: 当发出MAX_VALUE或MIN_VALUE改变。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when min_value, max_value, page, or step change.
trans-unit.target: 当发出MIN_VALUE，MAX_VALUE，网页，或一步变化。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when value changes.
trans-unit.target: 值更改时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when sleeping changes.
trans-unit.target: 睡觉时发出的变化。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when PopupMenu of this MenuButton is about to show.
trans-unit.target: 在此MenuButton的PopupMenu即将显示时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a PhysicsBody object enters, reporting which shapes overlapped.
trans-unit.target: 在输入PhysicsBody对象时发出，报告哪些形状重叠。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a PhysicsBody object enters.
trans-unit.target: 在输入PhysicsBody对象时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a PhysicsBody object exits, reporting which shapes were overlapping.
trans-unit.target: 当PhysicsBody对象退出时发出，报告哪些形状重叠。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a PhysicsBody object exits.
trans-unit.target: 当PhysicsBody对象退出时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a PhysicsBody2D object enters, reporting which shapes overlapped.
trans-unit.target: 在输入PhysicsBody2D对象时发出，报告哪些形状重叠。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a PhysicsBody2D object enters.
trans-unit.target: 在输入PhysicsBody2D对象时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a PhysicsBody2D object exits, reporting which shapes were overlapping.
trans-unit.target: 当PhysicsBody2D对象退出时发出，报告哪些形状重叠。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a PhysicsBody2D object exits.
trans-unit.target: 当PhysicsBody2D对象退出时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a GraphNode is selected.
trans-unit.target: 选择 GraphNode 时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a WebSocket message is received. Note: This signal is NOT emitted when used as high level multiplayer peer.
trans-unit.target: 收到WebSocket消息时发出。注意:当用作高级多人对等时,不会发出此信号。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a body enters into contact with this one. contact_monitor must be true and contacts_reported greater than 0.
trans-unit.target: 当物体与该物体接触时发出。contact_monitor必须是 true 和contacts_reported大于 0 。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a body enters into contact with this one. Contact monitor and contacts reported must be enabled for this to work.
trans-unit.target: 当一个物体与此物体接触时发出。必须启用接触监测和接触报告功能,才能发挥作用。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a body enters into contact with this one. Reports colliding shape information. See CollisionObject2D for shape index information. contact_monitor must be true and contacts_reported greater than 0.
trans-unit.target: 当物体与该物体接触时发出。报告碰撞形状信息。有关形状索引信息，请参见CollisionObject2D。contact_monitor必须是 true 和contacts_reported大于 0 。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a body exits contact with this one. contact_monitor must be true and contacts_reported greater than 0.
trans-unit.target: 当物体退出与该物体的接触时发出。contact_monitor必须是 true 和contacts_reported大于 0 。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a body shape exits contact with this one. Contact monitor and contacts reported must be enabled for this to work.
trans-unit.target: 当一个体型与本体接触后发出。必须启用接触监测和报告的接触点,才能使用。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a body shape exits contact with this one. Reports colliding shape information. See CollisionObject2D for shape index information. contact_monitor must be true and contacts_reported greater than 0.
trans-unit.target: 当身体形状退出与该形状的接触时发出。报告碰撞形状信息。有关形状索引信息，请参见CollisionObject2D。contact_monitor必须是 true 和contacts_reported大于 0 。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a breakpoint is placed via the breakpoint gutter.
trans-unit.target: 通过断点沟放置断点时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a button on the tree was pressed (see TreeItem.add_button).
trans-unit.target: 在按下树上的按钮时发出（请参见TreeItem.add_button）。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a button on this controller is pressed.
trans-unit.target: 当按下该控制器上的按钮时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a button on this controller is released.
trans-unit.target: 释放本控制器上的按钮时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a cell is selected.
trans-unit.target: 选择单元格时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a cell with the TreeItem.CELL_MODE_CUSTOM is clicked to be edited.
trans-unit.target: 单击带有TreeItem.CELL_MODE_CUSTOM的单元格进行编辑时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a client disconnects. was_clean_close will be true if the connection was shutdown cleanly.
trans-unit.target: 客户端断开连接时发出。如果干净地关闭了连接， was_clean_close 将为 true 。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a client requests a clean close. You should keep polling until you get a client_disconnected signal with the same id to achieve the clean close. See WebSocketPeer.close for more details.
trans-unit.target: 当客户端请求干净关闭时发出。您应该继续轮询，直到获得具有相同 id 的client_disconnected信号以完成清理关闭。有关更多详细信息，请参见WebSocketPeer.close。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a column’s title is pressed.
trans-unit.target: 按下列标题时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a connection attempt fails.
trans-unit.target: 连接尝试失败时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a connection attempt succeeds.
trans-unit.target: 连接尝试成功时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a connection with the server is established, protocol will contain the sub-protocol agreed with the server.
trans-unit.target: 与服务器建立连接时发出， protocol 将包含与服务器达成协议的子协议。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a custom Visual Script node is added or removed.
trans-unit.target: 添加或删除自定义Visual Script节点时发出。

trans-unit.source: Emitted when a custom button is pressed. See add_button.
trans-unit.target: 按下自定义按钮时发出。参见add_button。
